|width=200|lines=3
|File:Mission Control Celebrates - GPN-2000-001313.jpg|alt2=Mission Control celebrates the successful splashdown of Apollo 13|Mission Control celebrates the successful splashdown of Apollo 13
|File:Jim Lovell newspaper.jpg|alt3=James A. Lovell reads newspaper account of Apollo 13|Commander James A. Lovell, Jr. reads a newspaper account of the safe recovery of Apollo 13
